`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`
- **Mode-aware centering**: `handleCenter` checks `isGrid` to use the correct CSS properties вҖ” `justify-items` for grid vs `justify-content` for flex. This mirrors how the existing `AlignBox` component already handles this distinction.
- **Undo atomicity**: Both handlers call `beginBatch()` before any `apply()` calls and `endBatch()` after. The batch system in `apply.ts` uses a depth counter (`batchDepth`), so nested batches are safe вҖ” it only flushes when depth returns to 0.
- **PILL_BUTTON reuse**: The buttons use the existing `PILL_BUTTON` style constant from `panelStyles.ts`, keeping visual consistency with the rest of the panel.
`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`

